"1 1/2 pounds green beans, stems trimmed and cut into 1 1/2-in. lengths","16 ounces whole-grain penne, rotini, rotelle, or fusilli pasta","1/2 cup mayonnaise","  About 1/3 lb. Roquefort cheese","2 tablespoons red wine vinegar","3 tablespoons each finely chopped flat-leaf parsley and finely chopped chives","5  crisply cooked thick slices bacon, crumbled","1/2 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","  Salt"